elements.name: Como un usuario inicio sesión y creo un post con footer html

steps.name: I set text "<USERNAME>" on element with xpath "<USERNAME_EID>"
I set text "<PASSWORD>" on element with xpath "<PASSWORD_EID>"
I set text "POST con FOOTER" on element with xpath "<POST_TITLE_ECLASS>"
I set text "Hey post has sido creado" on element with xpath "<CONTENT_ECLASS>"
I set text "<HTML_TEXT_FOOTER>" on element with xpath "<CODE_INJ_TEXT>"
